TextEng: Sounds bad. What's your name?
There, there, fellow. It'll be all right. May I ask you some questions?
Text: 괜찮아요, 친구. 다 잘될 거예요. 몇 가지 물어봐도 될까요?

TextEng: Don't you think you're a little old to be crying like that? What's your name?
Text: 그렇게 울기엔 좀 나이가 있지 않아? 이름이 뭐야?

TextEng: Uh, don't worry, maybe I can help. Why don't you answer some questions for me first?
Text: 어, 걱정 마, 내가 도와줄 수 있을지도 몰라. 먼저 몇 가지 질문에 대답해 줄래?

TextEng: Oh quit your blubbering and tell me who you are.
Yeah, whatever. I have a question.
You so sad. Who you?
Me have questions.
Goodbye.
Call me <FirstName>.
My name is <FullName>. Pleased to meet you, Revat.
I'm not sure I want to tell you my name right now.
Text: 지금 당장 이름을 말하고 싶지는 않아.

TextEng: Me is <FirstName>.
Me called <FullName>. Is nice to meet you.
Me not want tell.
What's so terrible about today?
What bad about today?
Why don't you start by telling me who you are?
Who you?
Don't you think the trolls would have eaten your mom?
Text: 트롤들이 네 엄마를 먹어버렸을 거라고 생각 안 해?

TextEng: Where would they be keeping your mom?
What would you pay to get your mom back?
Don't worry, I'll save her for you.
I wish I could help, but I'm busy right now.
You Momma be eaten maybe?
You know where she being held?
You pay for rescue maybe?
Me help you. Me save the mom.
Nope. Me too busy.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> All right, but I think I might need some money now, to help me rescue your mom.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 좋아, 근데 엄마를 구하려면 지금 돈이 좀 필요할 것 같아.

TextEng: Fine. But you better pay me some up front, or maybe Momma won't come back ever!
Text: 좋아. 근데 선불로 좀 줘, 안 그러면 엄마가 영영 못 돌아올 수도 있어!

TextEng: I'll do what I can.
Momma will be returned safe and sound, I promise.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me need some coin now to help save Momma.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 엄마 구하려면 지금 돈 좀 필요해.

TextEng: Me want coin now. You give gold or Momma not get back maybe!
Text: 나 지금 돈 줘. 금화 안 주면 엄마 못 돌아올지도!

TextEng: Me do that.
You Momma come back safe soon. Me promise!
Text: 너 엄마 곧 무사히 돌아와. 나 약속!

TextEng: Tell me again where I can find her?
Text: 어디서 찾을 수 있는지 다시 말해줄래?

TextEng: I will keep looking for her.
I'm so sorry my good man, but your Momma died while I was trying to save her from the trolls.
Text: 정말 미안해, 친구. 트롤들한테서 구하려다가 네 엄마가 돌아가셨어.

TextEng: I did, but she was killed. Them's the breaks.
Text: 구했어, 근데 죽었어. 어쩔 수 없었어.

TextEng: Not yet, but I'm working on it.
Yeah, yeah, I'll get around to it eventually.
Say where she is again? Me forget.
Me keep looking for you Momma.
Me so sorry... but she die when me freeing her...
Text: 나 너무 미안... 근데 구할 때 죽었어...

TextEng: Me free her, but she die on way. (belch!) Oh well.
Text: 나 풀어줬어, 근데 오다가 죽었어. (꺼억!) 뭐 어쩔 수 없지.

TextEng: No, but me working on it.
Me get around to it sometime, maybe.
Tell me where she can be found.
You tell me where she be.
Not yet, but I'm working on it.
Yeah, yeah, I'll get around to it eventually.
No, but me working on it.
Me get around to it sometime, maybe.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Do you think your Momma is only worth 300 gp?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 네 엄마가 금화 300개밖에 가치가 없다고 생각해?

TextEng: I hate to call you stupid, but I think we agreed on more than that.
Text: 바보라고 부르긴 싫지만, 우리 그것보다 더 주기로 했잖아.

TextEng: Thank you. That will be fine.
No, there's no need for the reward. I was happy to do it.
Text: 아니, 보상은 필요 없어. 당연한 일이야.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me thinks you could try. You love you Momma, right?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 생각에 너 더 줄 수 있어. 너 엄마 사랑하지, 맞지?

TextEng: What, you stupid? Not what we said. You said me get more.
Text: 뭐, 너 바보야? 우리 그렇게 말 안 했어. 너 더 준다고 했어.

TextEng: This is okay.
No, me no need reward. Me happy to help.
Text: 아니, 나 보상 필요 없어. 나 기꺼이 도와.

TextEng: Sorry, you've made a mistake. I'm not with <CUSTOM2401>.
Text: 미안, 착각한 것 같아. 난 <CUSTOM2401> 소속 아니야.

TextEng: Yes, I'm with <CUSTOM2401>.
Me not with <CUSTOM2401>.
Yep, me with <CUSTOM2401>.
Maybe I could help, if you tell me what you're talking about.
Text: 무슨 말인지 알려주면 내가 도와줄 수 있을지도.

TextEng: Me could help, if you say what me need do.
Text: 뭐 해야 하는지 말하면 나 도울 수 있어.

TextEng: Why? What went wrong?
Like that should surprise me?
What go wrong?
You screw up badder than me.
The trolls that Jax told me about.
And so like a great warrior, you ran away.
Trolls be nasty.
So like coward, you run away?
I have decided I will save your mother.
Nevermind.
Me decide me save the Momma.
Could you tell me what happened again?
You tell me you story 'gain.
